title: Ibrahima Koné (footballer, born 1969)
text: Ibrahima Koné (born 26 July 1969) is a former Ivorian <a href="Association%20football">footballer</a> who played as a <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a> for various clubs and the <a href="Ivory%20Coast%20national%20football%20team">Ivory Coast national football team</a>.
